name: Enceladus (itch) (Mahmood J, Edd3, DaKid)
description:
Description:

You're an alien creature who has traveled to the planet Enceladus. But it's a short tour, so you need to have as much fun as possible in this short span. But how?! Your race is much stimulated by speeding up and collecting weird alien amoebas. So make sure to do that!

Controls:

Left & Right Arrow keys ---> Move Horizontal

Up Arrow key ---> Ascend

Credits:

MahmoodJ - Design & Code

DaKid - Graphics & Animations

eDject - Sounds & Music
